@
text
@d1 1
a1 1
.\"	$OpenBSD: makefs.8,v 1.5 2016/10/17 07:45:32 natano Exp $
a44 1
.Op Fl B Ar endian
a67 16
.It Fl B Ar endian
Set the byte order of the image to
.Ar endian .
Valid byte orders are
.Ql 4321 ,
.Ql big ,
or
.Ql be
for big endian, and
.Ql 1234 ,
.Ql little ,
or
.Ql le
for little endian.
Some file systems may have a fixed byte order; in those cases this
argument will be ignored.
@


